|ShortSummary    = Tom makes an audition video to convince producers to give him and his friends their own reality show. However, Tom believes their video to be unconvincing, and tries to trick Santa Claus into making a video endorsing the friends. Santa Claus suggests that Tom and the friends make their own show.
|LineColor       = #000080
