Season 3 (2018)
This season was meant to be the second half of season 2, but it was later split into two separate seasons. This is the last season to be animated by Arx Anima. As of season 4, the show was animated with People Moving Pixels, with the transitions dropped. This is also the last season where the characters are seen without clothes.
